# The backend's origin (no path). Leave unset for local dev — the Vite
# dev-server proxy (see vite.config.ts) forwards relative /api/v1 requests to
# http://localhost:3000. In production (Vercel), set this to the deployed
# backend's origin, e.g.:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL="https://tankha-api.onrender.com"
#
# A trailing /api/v1 is stripped automatically if you include it by mistake
# (every generated API path already carries that prefix) — but the origin-only
# form above is the canonical one.
